    "en": {
      "title": "Inflation peaked in August",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Headline inflation for August, as measured by the year-on-year change in the Colombo Consumer Price Index, rose to 64.3%, the Department of Value and Statistics said.",
        "Inflation rose to 64.3% in August from 60.8% in July.",
        "Food inflation rose to 93.7% in August from 90.9% in July and non-food inflation rose to 50.2% from 46.5% in July, the department said.",
        "Food items increased by 0.83% and non-food items by 1.62%."
